  "description": "Dense partial cloud with minimal synchrony. 48 partials spread wide through stereo field, each drifting on its own phase trajectory. Very slow LFO1 on formant creates a glacial vowel drift through the fog. High breath adds turbulent air. Like hearing a choir through heavy mist at a great distance.",
